high_descs: Turn left, then left again to face the table.
Pick up the brown plate off of the table.
Turn around and walk towards the kitchen sink.
Put the brown plate in the sink, fill it with water, then pick it up.
Turn left and head towards the white table.
Place the brown plate full of water on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl full of water on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the table.
Pick up a wooden bowl from the table.
Turn back around and walk towards the sink.
Fill up the bowl with water from the sink.
Turn to your right and walk towards the table.
Place the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl filled with water on a table.

high_descs: Go to small dining table with tomato
Pick up square container from table
Place container in sink, turn on water, pick up filled container
Place filled pan on table with toaster
